Invocation Name: stay fit
des:
Welcome to Stay fit. This is a fitness Skill.

Here we are providing the user with the options of 4 categories 
cardio,
Abs,
full body, and
yoga,

all these exercises can be done at home, without any equipments.
exercises are generated by the system the user just have to select the dificulty level from easy, medium and hard.

Hope you guys will enjoy this skill and stay fit.

Note:This is the first version of the skill. We will keep improving this skill based on the user feedbacks
